reviewText: Dont be fooled you won't recieve the American Pride Collection I fell for this and recieved one dvd of the collection Goodwill Industries simply told me to return the dvd for a refund (from Australia) thats all good and well the point is I really looked forward to this collection arriving (as like advertised in the picture)
I gave this series to my dad as a gift.  Him and my boys watched it for hours.  They loved it...therefore, I love it!
..I won't rate these any more if you try to force a minimum amount of words. I don't have time. thx
